, finally, the check arrived. my jaw nearly fell on the floor. three of us girls drank 7 frozen cosmos and ate 3 appetizers... for $40. how is that even possible? if i had known in advance that the frozen cosmos were $3/each, i might have just chugged them and taken a cab home.\u000a\u000aneedless to say, i'll be back!
