 it's good to know that penn brewery's menu isn't entirely comprised of heavy german food, a common sin of restaurants that specialize in or feature german food.\u000a\u000ai definitely plan on stopping in to sample more of their sandwiches, appetizers and burgers the next time i want to go out for lunch - just thinking about trying their deutschtaun burger and their flatbreads makes my mouth water!
